schools.name: R M Marrs Magnet Middle School

data.description: This cute 2 bedroom bungalow has had a major glowup! Built in 1885 this home still retains some of the unique architectural details of the time, but has had several thoughtful modern upgrades throughout. As you enter you'll notice the upgraded LVP flooring througout and neutral paint showcasing the deco-styled arched doorways. Newer windows provide ample natural light. The kitchen boasts granite counters, tiled backsplash and a breakfast bar. Stainless steel appliances with gas stove. The two bedrooms have wood laminate flooring and ceiling fans. The full bath is fully tiled and features a charming pedestal sink and brushed nickel hardware. Laundry in the full lower level with potential for future finish! Exit to the extra deep, partially fenced rear yard with parking pad and alley access. Vinyl siding. Convenient location to I-80, the Henry Doorly Zoo, Lauritzen Gardens and several dining establishments. Be sure to check this great value out before it's sold!
